ederal-funds-rate%5C%22%3Efederal%20funds%20rate%3C%2Fa%3E.%20While%20mortgage%20rates%20aren't%20directly%20impacted%20by%20the%20Fed's%20benchmark%20rate%2C%20they%20often%20trend%20up%20or%20down%20based%20on%20how%20investors%20expect%20Fed%20policy%20moves%20to%20impact%20the%20broader%20economy.%20Once%20central%20bankers%20cut%20rates%2C%20mortgage%20rates%20are%20expected%20to%20go%20down%20somewhat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EMortgage%20Rates%20Today%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch2%3EMortgage%20Refinance%20Rates%20Today%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%3EMortgage%20Calculator%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EUse%20our%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20data-analytics-module%3D%5C%22body_link%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%2240%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fmortgage-calculator%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efree%20mortgage%20calculator%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0to%20see%20how%20today's%20mortgage%20rates%20will%20affect%20your%20monthly%20and%20long-term%20payments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20plugging%20in%20different%20term%20lengths%20and%20interest%20rates%2C%20you'll%20see%20how%20your%20monthly%20payment%20could%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E30-Year%20Fixed%20Mortgage%20Rates%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20average%2030-year%20fixed%20mortgage%20rate%20was%206.86%25%20last%20week%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.freddiemac.com%2Fpmms%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFreddie%20Mac%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20is%20one%20basis%20point%20lower%20than%20it%20was%20the%20week%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2030-year%20fixed-rate%20mortgage%20is%20the%20most%20common%20type%20of%20home%20loan.%20With%20this%20type%20of%20mortgage%2C%20you'll%20pay%20back%20what%20you%20borrowed%20over%2030%20years%2C%20and%20your%20interest%20rate%20won't%20change%20for%20the%20life%20of%20the%20loan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lengthy%2030-year%20term%20allows%20you%20to%20spread%20out%20your%20payments%20over%20a%20long%20period%20of%20time%2C%