%20become%20part%20of%20a%20hidden%20movement%20that%20went%20far%20beyond%20her%20Chicago%20publishing%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAcross%20the%20globe%2C%20a%20wave%20of%20workers%20are%20secretly%20outsourcing%20parts%20or%20all%20of%20their%20jobs.%20Labor%20has%20never%20been%20easier%20to%20invisibly%20offload%2C%20thanks%20to%20a%20perfect%20storm%20of%20factors%3A%20globalized%20social%20networks%2C%20ubiquitous%20software%20tools%2C%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fcovid-19%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epandemic%3C%2Fa%3E.%20An%20inadvertent%20byproduct%20of%20the%20rapacious%2C%20profit-seeking%20impulse%20that%20drives%20our%20global%20economy%2C%20this%20corporate%20subterfuge%20stretches%20from%20high-powered%20Silicon%20Valley%20techies%20to%20legions%20of%20low-paid%20helpers%20in%20India%20and%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWelcome%20to%20the%20world%20of%20shadow%20stand-ins.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EStories%20about%20covert%20outsourcing%20are%20nothing%20new.%20Essay%20mills%20and%20faux%20test-taking%20have%20become%20perennial%20problems%20in%20academia%2C%20and%20gig-economy%20workers%20are%20occasionally%20caught%20lending%20their%20accounts%20to%20friends.%20Walter%20Keane%20gained%20notoriety%20in%20the%201960s%20for%20passing%20off%20%26quot%3Bbig%20eyes%26quot%3B%20paintings%20by%20his%20wife%2C%20Margaret%2C%20as%20his%20own.%20In%202012%2C%20a%20Verizon%20engineer%20was%20caught%20farming%20out%20his%20work%20to%20a%20team%20in%20China%20so%20he%20could%20browse%20Reddit%20all%20day.%20But%20in%20most%20workplaces%2C%20the%20idea%20of%20hiring%20someone%20to%20do%20your%20job%20for%20you%20seemed%20so%20outlandish%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DrYaZ57Bn4pQ%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Onion%20satirized%20it%20in%202009%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20the%20natural%20endpoint%20to%20globalization%20and%20American%20laziness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20longer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20talked%20to%20dozens%20of%20players%20in%20the%20shadow%20stand-in%20economy%2C%20including%20people%20like%20Remi%2C%20hired%20helpers%2C%20and%20those%20who%20have%20watched%20colleagues%20or%20friends%20partake.%20(Citing%20reputational%20or%20professional%20risks%2C%20most%20spoke%20on%20condition%20of%20anonymity%20or%20asked%20to%20be%20identified%20only%20by%20their%20first%20or%20middle%20name.)%20Given%20its%20clandestine%20nature%2C%20it's%20difficult%20to%20know%20just%20how%20many%20people%20the%20network%20scoops%20up.%20But%20providers%20told%20me%20they%20had%20seen%20a%20surge%20in%20popularity%20since%202020%2C%20a%20consequence%20of%20the%20pandemic%20and%20its%20attendant%20remote-work%20revolution.%20The%20past%20four%20years%20have%20transformed%20workplace%20norms%2C%20liberating%20millions%20from%20commutes%20and%20precipitating%20a%20wave%20of%20alienation%20from%20professional%20life%20%E2%80%94%20while%20providing%20eye-watering%20opportunities%20for%20the%20hungry%20or%20unscrupulous.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20becomes%20very%20easy%20for%20people%20to%20take%20the%20support%20when%20working%20from%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20one%20shadow%20stand-in%20who%20lives%20in%20India%20and%20who%20has%20been%20in%20business%20since%202019.%20%26quot%3BAfter%20the%20pandemic%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20another%20from%20Pakistan%2C%20the%20industry%20%26quot%3Bboomed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20no%20one%20model%20for%20how%20shadow%20stand-ins%20work%2C%20and%20practitioners%20use%20different%20terms%3A%20outsourcing%2C%20delegating%2C%20proxy%20work%2C%20subcontracting%2C%20virtual%20assistants%2C%20offshoring%2C%20or%20the%20delightfully%20euphemistic%20%26quot%3Bjob%20support.%26quot%3B%20It%20ranges%20from%20doling%20out%20small%20tasks%20to%20providing%20someone%20login%20credentials%20for%20full%20remote%20access.%20Some%20people%20want%20a%20mentor%2C%20some%20want%20a%20crutch%20after%20using%20%3Ca%20h