rked%20up%20over.%20Sean%20and%20I%20were%20already%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmarried-couple-doesnt-live-together-anymore-it-improved-relationship-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Enon-traditional%20couple%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20having%20explored%20nonmonogamy%20in%20the%20past.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERegardless%20of%20our%20unconventional%20ways%2C%20Sean%20bought%20me%20the%20perfect%20wedding%20ring%20%E2%80%94%20two%20silver%20cats%20surrounding%20a%20white%20gold%20diamond.%20He%20couldn't%20find%20a%20ring%20he%20wanted%2C%20so%20he%20asked%20me%20to%20make%20one%20with%20epoxy%20resin.%20I%20did%2C%20but%20it%20didn't%20fit%20him%20and%20he%20didn't%20press%20me%20to%20make%20another%20one.%20I%20took%20his%20nonchalant%20attitude%20personally%20when%2C%20in%20reality%2C%20he%20just%20had%20less%20attachment%20to%20the%20idea%20of%20wearing%20a%20ring.%20Eventually%2C%20I%20also%20stopped%20wearing%20mine.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22293e02d4-4f08-49e4-9261-0a34e55c1676%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20worried%20what%20my%20family%20and%20friends%20would%20say%20when%20I%20took%20my%20ring%20off%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20after%20becoming%20less%20attached%20to%20my%20ring%2C%20I%20worried%20what%20others%20would%20think.%20I%20wondered%20whether%20my%20family%20and%20friends%20would%20notice%20and%2C%20if%20they%20did%2C%20how%20they%20would%20perceive%20us%20as%20a%20couple.%20I%20felt%20the%20love%20I%20shared%20with%20my%20partner%20might%20come%20into%20question.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20fear%20of%20judgment%20was%20impacting%20my%20choice%20to%20wear%20a%20ring.%20It%20was%20also%20affecting%20my%20ability%20to%20act%20on%20my%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpolyamorous-wedding-commitment-ring-relationships-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edesire%20to%20be%20polyamorous%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20But%20since%20I%20had%20worked%20through%20the%20shame%20that%20came%20with%20going%20against%20the%20societal%20expectation%20to%20wear%20a%20wedding%20ring%2C%20I%20thought%20we%20might%20be%20ready%20to%20try%20nonmonogamy%20again.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22329167c9-f32e-4181-a971-a6333de926bb%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20me%2C%20being%20in%20a%20nonmonogamous%20dynamic%20is%20an%20act%20of%20radical%20love%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20an%20abolitionist%2C%20I%20work%20to%20decolonize%20my%20mind%20and%20my%20relationships.%20I'm%20not%20the%20type%20of%20person%20to%20claim%20ownership%20over%20another.%20To%20me%2C%20that%20is%20exactly%20what%20wearing%20a%20wedding%20ring%20symbolized%3A%20Sean%20as%20my%20property.%20I%20didn't%20want%20that%20for%20us%2C%20and%20he%20didn't%20either.%20Once%20the%20ring%20came%20off%20and%20my%20research%20brain%20turned%20on%2C%20I%20read%20more%20about%20polyamory%2C%20starting%20with%20books%20like%20%26quot%3BThe%20Ethical%20Slut%3A%20A%20Practical%20Guide%20to%20Polyamory%2C%20Open%20Relationships%20%26amp%3B%20Other%20Adventures''%20and%20%26quot%3BPolysecure%3A%20Attachment%2C%20Trauma%20and%20Consensual%20Nonmonogamy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpolyamorous-couple-used-agile-scrum-to-improve-communication-jealousy-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edifficult%20aspect%20of%20polyamory%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20working%20through%20the%20insecurities%20you%20have%20to%20just%20get%20started.%20There%20are%20no%20rigid%20rules%20or%20structures%2C%20just%20rough%20guidelines.%20You%20figure%20it%20out%20as%20you%20go%20and%20will%20likely%20hit%20some%20bumps%20and%20potholes%20along%20the%20way.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20Sean%20and%20me%2C%20being%20in%20a%20nonmonogamous%20relationship%20means%20we%20can%20be%20intimately%20connected%20with%20others%2C%20both%20sexually%20and%20emotionally.%20Every%20new%20relationship%20encourages%20introspection%20and%20growth.%20Sure%2C%20you%20can%20get%20that%20in%20monogamy%2C%20but%20we're%20bound%20to%20learn%20more%20from%20multiple%20relationships.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnon-monogamy-terms-guide-definitions-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ENonmonogamy%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20a%20way%20for%20us%20to%20celebrate%20our%20love.%20Although%20insecurities%20come%20up%20%E2%80%94%20including%20some%20I%20never%20thought%20I%20had%20%E2%80%94%20there%20are%20good%20feelings%2C%20like%20compersion%2C%20which%20is%20when%20a%20person%20feels%20joy%20from%20seeing%20their%20partner%20happy%2C%20whether%20or%20not%20that%20happiness%20involves%20them%20directly.%20Working%20through%20the%20guilt%20I%20felt%20for%20not%20conforming%20to%20societal%20norms%20was%20liberating%2C%20and%20I%20continue%20to%20learn%20more%20about%20myself%20every%20day.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstopped-wearing-wedding-rings-nonmonogamous-polyamorous-relationship-marriage-2024-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719740822000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F667c703a40cf2af6e4f6042a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstopped-wearing-wedding-rings-nonmonogamous-polyamorous-relationship-marriage-2024-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22My%20husband%20and%20I%20were%20monogamous%20before%20we%20got%20married.%20When%20we%20stopped%20wearing%20our%20wedding%20rings%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20try%20polyamory.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Sara%20Ali)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstopped-wearing-wedding-rings-nonmonogamous-polyamorous-relationship-marriage-2024-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Italian%20officials%20will%20pay%20up%20to%20%2432%2C000%20for%20you%20to%20move%20to%20Tuscany%20%E2%80%94%20but%20there's%20a%20catch%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225412%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20view%20of%20the%20countryside%20in%20Tuscany%2C%20Italy%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F668077541f0c1cd6d73008cf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223661%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EItaly's%20new%20%26quot%3Bresidency%20in%20the%20mountains%26quot%3B%20program%20will%20pay%20people%20up%20to%20%2432%2C000%20to%20relocate%20to%20rural%20Tuscany%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20stabilize%20its%20population%20problem.%3Cp%3ESlim%20Aarons%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ETuscan%20officials%20created%20a%20%243%2C000%2C000%20fund%20to%20incentivize%20people%20to%20move%20to%20the%20rural%20countryside.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20fund%20will%20pay%20people%20grants%20of%20up%20to%20%2432%2C000%20to%20move%20to%20Tuscany%20and%20fix%20up%20a%20home%20there.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20grants%20will%20pay%2050%25%20of%20the%20costs%20of%20renovations.%20Applicants%20must%20make%20the%20property%20their%20primary%20home.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EImagine%20waking%20up%20each%20morning%20to%20a%20view%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftuscany-americans-moving-italy-cost-of-living-slow-pace-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETuscan%20countryside%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20making%20your%20home%20in%20the%20romantic%20Italian%20region%20known%20for%20its%20dry%20red%20wine%2C%20medieval%20architecture%2C%20and%20groves%20of%20olive%20trees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20imagine%20getting%20paid%20to%20do%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETuscan%20officials%20launched%20a%20new%20%26quot%3BResidency%20in%20the%20Mountains%26quot%3B%20program%20in%20June.%20The%20program%20created%20a%20%E2%82%AC2%2C800%2C000%2C%20or%20about%20%243%2C001%2C740%2C%20fund%20to%20encourage%20people%20to%20move%20to%20the%20rural%20countryside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fund%2C%20part%20of%20an%20effort%20to%20stabilize%20the%20country's%20dwindling%20population%2C%20will%20pay%20people%20grants%20ranging%20from%20%E2%82%AC10%2C000%20to%20%E2%82%AC30%2C000%20(about%20%2410%2C720%20to%20about%20%2432%2C161)%20to%20move%20to%20Tuscany%20and%20fix%20up%20a%20home%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20purpose%20of%20the%20intervention%20is%20to%20favor%20and%20encourage%20the%20repopulation%20and%20socio-economic%20revitalization%20of%20mountain%20areas%2C%20acting%20in%20contrast%20to%20the%20marginalization%20of%20these%20areas%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20program's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.regione.toscana.it%2F-%2Fbando-residenzialit%25C3%25A0-in-montagna-2024-contributi-per-l-acquisto-di-un-immobile%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewebsite%3C%2Fa%3E%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20grants%20will%20pay%2050%25%20of%20the%20costs%20of%20renovations%20of%20a%20home%20in%20one%20of%2076%20Tuscan%20cities%20with%20fewer%20than%205%2C000%20residents%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0including%20San%20Casciano%20dei%20Bagni%2C%20known%20for%20its%20thermal%20pools%3B%20Caprese%20Michelangelo%2C%20the%20birthplace%20of%20the%20renaissance%20artist%20of%20the%20same%20name%3B%20and%20the%20island%20of%20Capraia%20Isola.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20program%20is%20open%20to%20Italians%2C%20EU%20residents%2C%20and%20non-EU%20citizens%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0so%20long%20as%20they%20have%20established%20long-term%20residency%20lasting%20no%20less%20than%2010%20years.%20Eligible%20applicants%20must%20commit%20to%20making%20the%20Tuscan%20property%20their%20primary%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApplications%20for%20the%20program%20close%20on%20July%2027.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20the%20Public%20Relations%20Office%20of%20Tuscany%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EItaly%20has%20for%20years%20experimented%20with%20various%20schemes%20to%20attract%20new%20residents%20to%20its%20rural%20regions.%20The%20country%2C%20which%20has%20Europe's%20smallest%20share%20of%20children%20under%20the%20age%20of%2015%2C%20faces%20a%20population%20crisis%20so%20significant%20that%20nearly%202%2C500%20towns%20are%20on%20the%20verge%20of%20collapse%20and%20will%20not%20survive%20more%20than%2025%20years%2C%20according%20to%20a%202016%20study%20released%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2017%2F09%2F07%2Ft-magazine%2Fabandoned-italian-towns.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EItaly's%20Ministry%20of%20Environment%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2Ftravel%2Farticle%2Fitalian-ghost-hamlet-san-severino%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECNN%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20last%20year%20that%20there%20are%20more%20than%206%2C000%20ghost%20villages%20around%20the%20country%2C%20left%20deserted%20due%20to%20migration%20and%20natural%20disasters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20in%202018%2C%20new%20residents%20in%20Molise%20were%20offered%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmolise-italy-offering-to-pay-people-27500-to-move-there-2019-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%2427%2C500%20to%20move%20to%20the%20abandoned%20towns%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20mountainous%20region%20on%20the%20country's%20eastern%20coast.%20The%20following%20year%2C%20officials%20in%20the%20town%20of%20Ollolai%20put%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmolise-italy-offering-to-pay-people-27500-to-move-there-2019-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E200%20homes%20on%20the%20market%20for%20%E2%82%AC1%3C%2Fa%3E%20(%241.25)%20each%20to%20avoid%20the%20same%20fate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESicily%20likewise%20went%20viral%20for%20offering%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphotos-italy-1-dollar-homes-need-a-lot-of-work-2019-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%241%20homes%20for%20sale%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%2C%20despite%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fitaly-old-houses-california-woman-purchase-3-bucks-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edesperate%20need%20for%20repair%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20attracted%20swarms%20of%20expats%20who%20flocked%20to%20the%20country%20to%20snap%20up%20one%20of%20the%20abandoned%20properties.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20previously%20reported%20that%20in%20Sicily%2C%20there%20were%20time%20limits%20for%20repairs%20to%20be%20completed%2C%20officials%20required%20buyers%20to%20work%20with%20specific%20contractors%20to%20finish%20the%20work%2C%20and%20renovations%20cost%20upwards%20of%20%2430%2C000%20to%20complete%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0but%20some%20buyers%20found%20it%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcalifornians-sicily-italy-one-euro-homes-expensive-properties-true-cost-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworth%20every%20penny%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fitaly-pays-to-move-tuscany-residence-in-mountains-2024-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719740822000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F668079691f0c1cd6d73008e3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fitaly-pays-to-move-tuscany-residence-in-mountains-2024-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Italy's%20new%20%26quot%3Bresidency%20in%20the%20mountains%26quot%3B%20program%20will%20pay%20people%20up%20to%20%2432%2C000%20to%20relocate%20to%20rural%20Tuscany%20to%20help%20stabilize%20its%20population.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ktangalakislippert%40businessinsider.com%20(Katherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fitaly-pays-to-move-tuscany-residence-in-mountains-2024-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Crystal%20ball%20economics%3A%20What%20psychics%20can%20tell%20us%20about%20America's%20spending%20habits%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223856%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Photo%20illustration%20of%20a%20bill%20floating%20in%20a%20crystal%20ball.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F667466c992f5cd1b99e66db7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221936%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHow%20much%20a%20psychic%20costs%20is%20part%20business%2C%20part%20...%20magic%3F%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3B%20Jenny%20Chang-Rodriguez%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20not%20sure%20whether%20I%20should%20feel%20guilty%20for%20not%20telling%20Jessica%20about%20the%20ulterior%20motives%20for%20my%20palm-reading%20visit.%20On%20the%20one%20hand%2C%20I%20probably%20should%20have%20said%20I%20was%20testing%20it%20out%20for%20a%20story.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20she's%20a%20psychic%2C%20so%20she%20should%20have%20intuited%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20didn't%2C%20which%20meant%20that%20on%20a%20warm%20June%20afternoon%20I%20found%20myself%20seated%20across%20from%20her%20in%20a%20sweaty%20little%20basement%20space%20in%20lower%20Manhattan.%20For%20%2425%2C%20which%20wound%20up%20being%20%2430%20because%20she%20didn't%20have%20change%2C%20Jessica%20told%20me%20my%20fortune.%20She%20said%20that%20I'm%20a%20kind%20person%20(true%2C%20I%20hope)%2C%20that%20I'm%20standoffish%20(also%20true%2C%20unfortunately)%2C%20and%20that%20I'm%20about%20to%20change%20jobs%20and%20move%20(no%20and%20no).%20She%20also%20said%20I'm%20afraid%20to%20express%20my%20creative%20side%20through%20activities%20like%20writing%2C%20which%20%E2%80%A6%20well.%20Toward%20the%20end%20of%20the%20reading%2C%20Jessica%20saw%20something%20darker%2C%20a%20negative%20energy%20holding%20me%20back.%20She%20suggested%20I%20consider%20a%20cleansing.%20The%20cost%3A%20%24500.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20you%20are%20likely%20rolling%20your%20eyes%2C%20but%20plenty%20of%20people%20are%20open%20to%20the%20idea%20of%20the%20paranormal.%20In%20a%202017%20survey%20of%20American%20adults%20by%20the%20Pew%20Research%20Center%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pewresearch.org%2Fshort-reads%2F2018%2F10%2F01%2Fnew-age-beliefs-common-among-both-religious-and-nonreligious-americans%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E41%25%20of%20respondents%20said%20they%20believed%20in%20psychics%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%2042%25%20said%20they%20thought%20spiritual%20energy%20could%20be%20located%20in%20physical%20things%2C%20and%2029%25%20said%20they%20believed%20in%20astrology.%20In%20a%202019%20IPSOS%20survey%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ipsos.com%2Fen-us%2Fnews-polls%2Fhalloween-2019%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enearly%20half%20of%20respondents%20said%20they%20believed%20in%20ghosts%3C%2Fa%3E.%20There's%20a%20line%20between%20believing%20in%20psychics%20and%20paying%20for%20them%2C%20but%20plenty%20of%20people%20do%20indeed%20pay%2C%20and%20even%20some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkate-tomas-corporate-psychic-business-hollywood-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebig%20businesses%20are%20willing%20to%20shell%20out%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20a%20consultation.%20According%20to%20IBISWorld%2C%20the%20psychic-services%20industry%20in%20the%20US%20is%20worth%20%242.3%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20took%20Jessica's%20card%20and%20told%20her%20I'd%20think%20about%20her%20proposition.%20I'm%20inclined%20to%20give%20her%20the%20benefit%20of%20the%20doubt%20that%20she%20trusts%20in%20her%20abilities%2C%20but%20even%20people%20I%20know%20who%20are%20into%20the%20psychic%20thing%20said%20this%20didn't%20sound%20legitimate%2C%20not%20like%20the%20%26quot%3Breal%26quot%3B%20psychics%20they%20go%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20defense%2C%20Jessica%20(whose%20name%20I%20changed%20here%20because%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20screw%20up%20her%20business)%20had%20her%20prices%20listed%20outside%20her%20shop%2C%20and%20upselling%20isn't%20a%20new%20phenomenon.%20It's%20a%20little%20mind-bending%20to%20think%20about%20how%20psychics%20go%20about%20setting%20prices%20%E2%80%94%20how%20they%20gauge%20fair%20costs%20for%20their%20services%2C%20decipher%20what%20customers%20will%20agree%20to%2C%20and%20use%20the%20opacity%20of%20the%20market%20to%20their%20advantage.%20It's%20not%20like%20there's%20some%20tarot%20price%20index%20or%20many%20materials%20that%20go%20into%20the%20work%20besides%20their%20supposed%20magical%20abilities.%20But%20for%20the%20most%20part%2C%20psychics%20rely%20on%20good%20old%20supply%20and%20demand%2C%20sprinkling%20in%20some%20extra%20tactics%20%E2%80%94%20mystical%20and%20not%20%E2%80%94%20to%20bring%20in%20profits.%20The%20%24500%20Jessica%20was%20asking%20for%20might%20seem%20worth%20it%20to%20a%20true%20believer.%20Had%20she%20gone%20lower%2C%20I%20might%20have%20said%20yes%20and%20paid%20%2450%20to%20get%20the%20devil%20off%20my%20back%2C%20just%20in%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EPsychic%20prices%20are%20all%20over%20the%20place.%20On%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fastrology-app-sanctuary-raises-millions-ignites-investor-vc-debate-2021-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESanctuary%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20app%20where%20you%20can%20find%20astrologists%20and%20mediums%2C%20many%20readings%20start%20at%20%245%20for%20five%20minutes%2C%20but%20then%20some%20people%20charge%20%243%20(or%20even%20%2413%20or%20%2420)%20per%20additional%20minute.%20The%20shops%20you%20see%20in%20major%20cities%20may%20advertise%20a%20price%20of%20%2410%20or%20%2425%2C%20but%20that's%20often%20just%20to%20get%20people%20in%20the%20door.%20Psychics%20and%20mediums%20haven't%20been%20immune%20to%20inflation%20either.%20Data%20provided%20to%20me%20by%20the%20online%20ticketing%20service%20Eventbrite%20indicates%20the%20average%20ticket%20price%20for%20psychic-related%20events%20in%20the%20US%20rose%20to%20%2444%20in%202023%20from%20%2439%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20reached%20out%20to%20a%20couple%20of%20psychics%20to%20get%20a%20sense%20of%20how%20they%20approached%20pricing%2C%20and%20you%20may%20not%20be%20surprised%20to%20learn%20that%20the%20answer%20wasn't%20straightforward.%20Some%20of%20it%20is%20basic%20business%20principles%2C%20but%20a%20lot%20of%20it%20is%20pretty%20woo-woo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMany%20of%20us%20live%20eccentric%20lifestyles%20to%20be%20permitted%20to%20exist%20the%20way%20that%20we%20do%20safely%20with%20one%20foot%20on%20either%20side%20of%20the%20veil%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Blue%20June%2C%20a%20tarot%20reader%20based%20in%20New%20York%2C%20adding%20that%20they%20had%20to%20keep%20%26quot%3Bregimented%20and%20sometimes%20unusual%20routines%26quot%3B%20to%20be%20accurate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJune%20said%20some%20of%20the%20parameters%20that%20determine%20price%20are%20quite%20mundane%3A%20experience%20and%20expertise%2C%20what%20nearby%20competitors%20charge%2C%20customer%20reviews%2C%20and%20overhead.%20But%20there%20are%20also%20some%20more%20mystic%20pieces%20to%20her%20pricing.%20She%20charges%20%2455.55%20to%20%24155.55%20for%20her%20services%20%E2%80%94%20a%20dream%20interpretation%20is%20her%20cheapest%20offer%2C%20while%20spellwork%20is%20the%20most%20expensive.%20(In%20numerology%2C%20555%20is%20an%20%26quot%3Bangel%20number%26quot%3B%20that%20symbolizes%20change%20and%20transformation.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BClients%20should%20not%20approach%20the%20inquiry%20of%20service%20prices%20with%20a%20gifted%20psychic%20in%20the%20same%20way%20they%20approach%20their%20grocery%20bill%2C%26quot%3B%20June%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20luxury%20service%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20and%20it%20cannot%20be%20defined%20in%20the%20same%20way%20as%20any%20other%20shopping%20can.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELisa%20Stardust%2C%20a%20New%20York-based%20astrologer%2C%20said%20she%20sometimes%20gives%20free%20readings%20to%20people%20if%20they're%20in%20pain%20or%20have%20a%20quick%20question%20%E2%80%94%20but%20like%20anyone%2C%20she%20has%20her%20limits.%20%26quot%3BThe%20thing%20about%20being%20so%20empathetic%20and%20having%20all%20of%20this%20sensitivity%20to%20the%20world%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20can%20take%20advantage%20of%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20charges%20%2450%20for%20one%20tarot%20question%20answered%20via%20email%20and%20%24200%20for%20a%20full%20astrological%20reading%2C%20though%20she%20says%20there's%20some%20wiggle%20room%20if%20people%20can't%20pay%20the%20full%20amount.%20She%20wants%20people%20to%20feel%20that%20they%20got%20their%20money's%20worth%2C%20she%20abides%20by%20a%20code%20of%20ethics%2C%20and%20this%20isn't%20her%20only%20stream%20of%20income.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20pushing%20services%20on%20people%20that%20they%20don't%20deserve%20or%20need%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20wouldn't%20be%20a%20supply%20of%20psychics%20out%20there%20charging%20money%20if%20there%20wasn't%20demand.%20Value%20ultimately%20comes%20down%20to%20how%20much%20someone%20is%20willing%20to%20pay.%20So%20why%20are%20people%20willing%20to%20pay%20for%20what's%20essentially%20a%20guess%20by%20a%20stranger%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENeil%20Dagnall%20and%20Ken%20Drinkwater%2C%20a%20pair%20of%20cognitive%20and%20parapsychological%20researchers%20at%20Manchester%20Metropolitan%20University%2C%20have%20spent%20years%20researching%20people's%20paranormal%20beliefs.%20They%20said%20one%20reason%20people%20engage%20with%20the%20paranormal%20is%20that%20they're%20searching%20for%20meaning.%20They%20want%20to%20resolve%20life's%20uncertainties%2C%20reaffirm%20their%20own%20beliefs%2C%20or%20gain%20a%20sense%20of%20closure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20people%20have%20got%20a%20bereavement%20and%20they%20go%20to%20a%20psychic%2C%20having%20some%20sort%20of%20contact%2C%20whether%20it's%20genuine%20or%20not%2C%20with%20somebody%20who's%20passed%20over%20actually%20is%20reassuring%20to%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20Dagnall%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMaybe%20I'm%20skeptical%2C%20but%20I'm%20not%20a%20debunker%2C%20by%20the%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20Drinkwater%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20end%20up%20being%20compassionate%20about%20people's%20experiences%20and%20think%20that%20they're%20real%20to%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20psychics%20are%20able%20to%20charge%20what%20may%20seem%20like%20exorbitant%20prices%20because%20people%20make%20inferences%20about%20quality%20based%20on%20price.%20Whatever%20our%20motivations%20for%20going%20for%20a%20psychic%20%E2%80%94%20we%20think%20they'll%20get%20us%20in%20touch%20with%20the%20dead%2C%20or%20we're%20just%20doing%20it%20for%20kicks%20%E2%80%94%20we%20don't%20want%20the%20low-budget%20version.%20There%20are%20limits%20here%2C%20because%20once%20you%20get%20to%20%24300%2C%20chances%20are%20you%20think%20it's%20real.%20But%20given%20a%20choice%20between%20a%20%241%20reading%20or%20a%20%2420%20reading%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20will%20spring%20for%20the%20%2420%20one%20because%20they%20figure%20it's%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20it's%20too%20cheap%2C%20people%20might%20assume%20that%20it's%20not%20good%2C%20that%20it%20actually%20isn't%20effective%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jane%20Risen%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20behavioral%20science%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Chicago's%20Booth%20School%20of%20Business%20who%20has%20studied%20why%20people%20might%20want%20magical%20products%20even%20if%20they%20don't%20entirely%20think%20they%20work.%20%26quot%3BIn%20some%20ways%2C%20putting%20the%20price%20on%20it%2C%20making%20people%20pay%20for%20it%2C%20can%20be%20part%20of%20why%20people%20think%20that%20it%20could%20work.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20really%20believe%20what%20the%20psychic%20will%20tell%20you%2C%20%3Cem%3Eof%20course%3C%2Fem%3E%20you're%20going%20to%20pay%20for%20it.%20But%20not%20everyone%20who%20goes%20to%20a%20psychic%20buys%20into%20it.%20For%20those%20in%20the%20latter%20camp%2C%20it%20may%20come%20down%20to%20emotional%20management%2C%20Risen%20said.%20You're%20pretty%20sure%20the%20psychic%20won't%20predict%20the%20future%20or%20solve%20your%20problems%2C%20but%20she%20might%20make%20you%20feel%20less%20worried.%20Risen's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.psychologicalscience.org%2Fnews%2Fknock-on-wood-certain-superstitious-actions-make-us-feel-better-study-shows.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresearch%3C%2Fa%3E%20suggests%20that%20while%20getting%20a%20psychic's%20services%20doesn't%20make%20the%20bad%20thing%20less%20likely%20(obviously)%2C%20it%20does%20make%20us%20less%20afraid%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20could%20imagine%20purchasing%20partially%20for%20the%20emotional%20management%20of%20it%20and%20partially%20because%20you%20feel%20like%2C%20'Well%2C%20I%20might%20as%20well%20be%20better%20safe%20than%20sorry%2C'%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20It%20isn't%20that%20different%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-we-knock-on-wood-origins-of-7-other-common-superstitions-psychology-magical-thinking-2018-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eknocking%20on%20wood%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20drinking%20that%20shot%20of%20apple%20cider%20vinegar%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20even%20though%20you%20can't%20remember%20what%20sort%20of%20ailment%20it's%20supposed%20to%20be%20alleviating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20should%20go%20without%20saying%20here%20that%20going%20to%20a%20psychic%20is%20often%20fun.%20Many%20people%20derive%20joy%20from%20having%20their%20fortunes%20told%20and%20toying%20with%20the%20possibility%20that%20what's%20said%20might%20be%20right.%20There's%20often%20a%20social%20element%2C%20too%20%E2%80%94%20people%20get%20their%20palms%20read%20with%20a%20group%20of%20friends.%20It's%20like%20when%20the%20lottery%20jackpot%20gets%20really%20high%20and%20everyone's%20buying%20tickets%20and%20fantasizing%20about%20what%20they'll%20do%20with%20their%20riches%2C%20even%20though%20they%20know%20they're%20not%20going%20to%20win.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20countless%20stories%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DWhMGcp9xIhY%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epsychic%20hoaxes%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20the%20early%202000s%2C%20the%20Federal%20Trade%20Commission%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ftc.gov%2Fnews-events%2Fnews%2Fpress-releases%2F2002%2F02%2Fftc-charges-miss-cleo-promoters-deceptive-advertising-billing-collection-practices%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edinged%20the%20TV%20psychic%20Miss%20Cleo%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20accusing%20her%20of%20engaging%20in%20deceptive%20advertising%20and%20billing%20practices.%20The%20faith%20healer%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fscam-everlasting-after-25-years-debunked-faith-healer-still-preaching-debt-relief-scam-2011-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPeter%20Popoff%3C%2Fa%3E%20would%20send%20his%20wife%20and%20staffers%20to%20chat%20with%20audience%20members%20before%20his%20sessions%20and%20then%20pass%20the%20intel%20on%20to%20him.%20But%20something%20doesn't%20have%20to%20be%20a%20scam%20to%20be%20harmful%20or%20predatory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPsychics%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20tools%20at%20their%20disposal%20to%20get%20more%20money%20out%20of%20people.%20They%20may%20inject%20a%20sense%20of%20urgency%20or%20scarcity%2C%20use%20a%20bait%20and%20switch%2C%20or%20hook%20you%20with%20a%20cheap%20service%20before%20upselling%20you.%20It's%20not%20that%20different%20from%20how%20a%20lot%20of%20businesses%20work%2C%20from%20car%20dealerships%20to%20e-commerce%20websites.%20On%20the%20one%20hand%2C%20if%20something%20feels%20good%20to%20someone%2C%20who%20is%20anyone%20to%20say%20it's%20bad%3F%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20these%20practices%20can%20become%20detrimental%20when%20people%20allow%20them%20to%20dictate%20their%20important%20life%20decisions.%20%26quot%3BMy%20psychic%20said%26quot%3B%20isn't%20a%20good%20reason%20to%20buy%20a%20stock%20or%20to%20end%20your%20marriage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20a%20person's%20buying%20into%20everything%20that%20person's%20telling%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Drinkwater%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bthat's%20problematic.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20and%20Dagnall%20told%20me%20that%20most%20of%20the%20psychics%20they'd%20interviewed%20really%20believed%20they%20had%20abilities%20and%20only%20a%20handful%20admitted%20they%20didn't.%20Many%20are%20skeptical%20of%20other%20psychics%3B%20they%20don't%20want%20the%20fakes%20out%20there%20giving%20them%20a%20bad%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenness%20is%20generally%20a%20positive%20quality%2C%20but%20some%20people%20are%20a%20little%20%3Cem%3Etoo%20%3C%2Fem%3Eopen%2C%20to%20the%20point%20they%20get%20taken%20advantage%20of%2C%20said%20Ralph%20Lewis%2C%20an%20associate%20professor%20in%20the%20psychiatry%20department%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Toronto%20who%20has%20an%20extracurricular%20interest%20in%20%26quot%3Bweird%26quot%3B%20beliefs.%20%26quot%3BSome%20people%20are%20very%20open%2C%20and%20some%20people%20are%20not%20very%20open%2C%20but%20too%20much%20openness%20equals%20gullibility%2C%20credulity%2C%20suggestibility%2C%20and%20so%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20go%20too%20far%2C%20then%20as%20the%20skeptics%20like%20to%20say%2C%20don't%20be%20so%20open-minded%20that%20your%20brain%20falls%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20all%20sorts%20of%20biases%20that%20make%20people%20believe%20in%20psychics%20when%20they%20shouldn't.%20There's%20hindsight%20bias%2C%20where%20we%20see%20past%20events%20as%20more%20predictable%20than%20they%20were.%20There's%20also%20our%20tendency%20to%20conflate%20correlation%20and%20causation%3A%20I%20give%20Jessica%20%24500%20for%20the%20cleansing%2C%20I%20get%20a%20promotion%20at%20work%2C%20and%20there%20I%20am%20a%20month%20later%20handing%20over%20another%20%24500%20even%20though%20the%20cleansing%20had%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20are%20free%20to%20spend%20their%20money%20any%20way%20they%20choose%2C%20and%20we're%20never%20going%20to%20stop%20them%20from%20wasting%20money%20on%20implausible%20products%2C%26quot%3B%20Lewis%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20I%20do%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20think%20that%20it's%20not%20just%20benign%20to%20let%20people%20have%20their%20magical%20beliefs%20and%20lead%20them%20unchallenged.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDagnall%20told%20me%20%E2%80%94%20while%20telling%20his%20coresearcher%20not%20to%20laugh%20%E2%80%94%20that%20at%20one%20point%20he%20started%20seeing%20a%20series%20of%20ones%20all%20over%20the%20place.%20He%20looked%20it%20up%20online%2C%20and%20supposedly%20it%20was%20his%20guardian%20angel%20telling%20him%20things%20were%20going%20to%20be%20fortuitous.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%2C%20I%20know%20it's%20not%20true%2C%20but%20it's%20just%20interesting%20that%20I%20was%20noticing%20that%20number%2C%20and%20I%20wanted%20to%20sort%20of%20then%20say%2C%20OK%2C%20well%2C%20if%20I%20was%20into%20the%20paranormal%2C%20what%20significance%20would%20it%20have%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20paranormal%20is%20quite%20seductive%20in%20that%20way%2C%20in%20that%20it%20can%20offer%20explanations%20for%20odd%2C%20anomalous%20things.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20coresearcher%20did%2C%20indeed%2C%20laugh.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20it's%20not%20obvious%20by%20now%2C%20I%20am%20a%20psychic%20skeptic.%20I've%20spent%20a%20few%20hundred%20dollars%20on%20mystical%20stuff%20over%20the%20years%20at%20the%20behest%20of%20friends%20%E2%80%94%20a%20psychic%20fair%20here%2C%20a%20crystal%20there%20%E2%80%94%20and%20have%20almost%20always%20felt%20disappointed.%20So%20while%20reporting%20for%20this%20story%2C%20I%20talked%20to%20a%20friend%20of%20a%20friend%20named%20Katy%20who's%20really%20into%20all%20of%20this%20to%20try%20to%20understand%20her%20motivations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKaty%20sees%20her%20shaman%20every%20month%20for%20%2480.%20%26quot%3BI%20literally%20run%20my%20life%20through%20her%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20me.%20She%20does%20monthly%20therapy%20through%20a%20psychic%20for%20%24105%20a%20session.%20That%20psychic%20is%20also%20a%20pet%20psychic%2C%20which%20is%20not%20Katy's%20jam.%20For%20her%20horoscope%2C%20Katy%20has%20a%20favorite%20YouTuber%20who%20works%20on%20tips.%20She%20sometimes%20stops%20for%20tarot%20readings%20at%20her%20local%20farmer's%20market.%20She%20sees%20it%20all%20as%20self-care.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20me%2C%20it's%20a%20part%20of%20my%20wellness%20routine%2C%26quot%3B%20Katy%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20just%20happens%20to%20be%20on%20my%20checklist.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%2C%20after%20an%20accident%20on%20her%20block%20in%20Chicago%2C%20Katy%20used%20a%20psychic%20to%20ensure%20the%20person%20had%20crossed%20over.%20Another%20time%2C%20she%20bought%20a%20bunch%20of%20bath%20oils%20in%20New%20York%20after%20a%20psychic%20told%20her%20she%20was%20cursed.%20She%20felt%20that%20only%20the%20latter%20episode%20was%20sketchy%3B%20I%20thought%20both%20were.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat's%20worth%20it%2C%20financially%2C%20for%20Katy%20would%20not%20be%20worth%20it%20for%20a%20lot%20of%20people.%20Once%20you%20get%20past%20necessities%2C%20that's%20true%20of%20a%20lot%20of%20things%2C%20whether%20it%20be%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhermes-became-ultimate-status-symbol-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBirkin%20bag%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstreaming%2Fhow-to-buy-taylor-swift-tour-tickets-concert-prices-compared%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETaylor%20Swift%20tickets%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20someone%20who%20says%20they%20can%20help%20you