20on%20their%20respective%20careers%20in%20the%20shortest%20format.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20have%20retired%20with%20the%20World%20Cup%20win%2C%20and%20probably%20better%20than%20any%20script%20that%20was%20written.%20Both%20players%20are%20great.%20They%20have%20done%20a%20lot%20for%20Indian%20cricket%2C%20and%20congratulate%20them%20and%20wish%20them%20all%20the%20best%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gambhir%20told%20PTI%20videos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Gambhir%20hoped%20that%20both%20the%20stalwarts%20would%20keep%20churning%20out%20grand%20performances%20in%20Tests%20and%20ODIs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20they%20are%20going%20to%20play%20two%20more%20formats%20%E2%80%93%20Test%20cricket%20and%20ODI%20cricket.%20I%20am%20sure%20they%20are%20going%20to%20keep%20contributing%20to%20the%20country%20and%20the%20team%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20former%20opener.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVeteran%20off-spinner%20R%20Ashwin%20termed%20Kohli%20a%20myth%20and%20recollected%20some%20of%20the%20best%20T20I%20innings%20by%20the%20star%20batter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CVirat%20Kohli%20has%20played%20his%20last%20T20%20game%2C%20and%20it%20has%20been%20a%20stellar%20career.%20The%20knocks%20I%20wanted%20to%20remember%20(of%20Kohli)%20are%3A%20the%20one%20against%20Australia%20in%20the%20quarterfinals%20(of%20the%202016%20T20%20WC)%20and%20against%20SA%20in%20the%202014%20T20%20WC%20semifinals.%20The%20man%20is%20actually%20a%20myth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhy%20I%20am%20not%20paying%20a%20big%20tribute%20to%20him%20because%20he%20has%20a%20long%20career%20ahead%20in%20two%20other%20formats.%20He%20has%20been%20playing%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Ashwin%20in%20his%20YouTube%20channel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20India%20pacer-turned-commentator%20Atul%20Wassan%20said%20Kohli%20and%20Rohit%20retired%20at%20the%20best%20possible%20time%2C%20so%20that%20the%20next%20line%20of%20cricketers%20can%20take%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20bound%20to%20happen.%20The%20team%20needs%20to%20focus%20on%20preparing%20for%20the%20next%20World%20Cup.%20They%20may%20be%20great%20players%2C%20but%20if%20they%20linger%2C%20it%20won't%20benefit%20the%20team.%20We%20need%20to%20pave%20the%20way%20for%20youngsters%20and%20groom%20them%20for%20the%20upcoming%20World%20Cup%2C%E2%80%9D%20Wassan%20told%20PTI%20videos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWassan%20said%20the%20decision%20of%20Kohli%20and%20Rohit%20will%20only%20benefit%20the%20team%20in%20the%20long-run.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20knew%20he%20(Virat%20Kohli)%20was%20going%20to%20retire.%20Age%20is%20catching%20up.%20We'll%20see%20them%20playing%20Test%20cricket%20and%20ODIs.%20T20%20requires%20specialists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20believe%20it's%20time%20for%20India%20to%20move%20forward%20from%20here.%20Once%20we've%20won%20the%20cup%2C%20it's%20best%20to%20progress%20further%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBCCI%20joint%20secretary%20Devajit%20Saikia%20said%20the%20victory%20will%20take%20Indian%20cricket%20to%20further%20heights%20despite%20two%20of%20the%20biggest%20stars%20moving%20away%20from%20T20Is.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFantastic%20win.%20I%20am%20sure%20this%20win%20will%20not%20only%20give%20a%20big%20boost%20to%20the%20development%20of%20cricket%20in%20India%20but%20in%20the%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20world%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRetirement%20is%20part%20and%20parcel%20of%20the%20game%20but%20this%20win%20has%20taken%20Indian%20cricket%20to%20a%20different%20level%20from%20today%20onwards%2C%E2%80%9D%20Saikia%20told%20PTI%20videos%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719739680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fsbbu1978_kohli-and-rohit_625x300_30_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2F