EThis%20is%20all%20%26quot%3BAI%20slop%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2024%2F06%2F11%2Fstyle%2Fai-search-slop.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enew%20term%3C%2Fa%3E%20describing%20the%20sudden%20flood%20of%20garbage%20AI-generated%20content%2C%20from%20ebooks%20to%20viral%20photos.%20Slop%20is%20everywhere%20on%20the%20internet%2C%20but%20its%20most%20pure%20version%20exists%20on%20Facebook.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbad-ai-art-is-overrunning-facebook-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShrimp%20Jesus%3C%2Fa%3E%20kind%20of%20slop%3A%20bizarre%2C%20obviously%20fake%2C%20and%20sometimes%20vaguely%20unsettling%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrypophobia-a-fear-of-holes-2015-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etrypophobia-triggering%3C%2Fa%3E%20way.%20Common%20themes%20involve%20old%20people%20holding%20a%20birthday%20cake%20asking%20you%20to%20wish%20them%20a%20happy%20birthday%3B%20babies%20doing%20things%20babies%20shouldn't%20do%3B%20snakes%20eating%20buses%2C%20bikes%2C%20or%20other%20vehicles%20overloaded%20with%20hundreds%20of%20babies%20or%20some%20other%20cargo%3B%20soldiers%20with%20prosthetic%20legs%3B%20women%20with%20missing%20limbs%20and%20huge%20busts%3B%20and%20Jesus.%20The%20images%20are%20often%20sort%20of%20eerily%20exploitative.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20tend%20to%20be%20posted%20on%20Facebook%20pages%20with%20generic-sounding%20names%20and%20captions%20that%20don't%20necessarily%20reflect%20the%20photo%2C%20like%20%26quot%3Bwhy%20don't%20photos%20like%20this%20ever%20trend%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bbeautiful%20cabin%20crew%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BScarlett%20Johansson%26quot%3B%20for%20an%20image%20of%20Jesus%20built%20into%20the%20hood%20of%20a%20car.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhy%20slop%3F%20The%20best%20explanation%20is%20that%20the%20Facebook%20pages%20posting%20these%20are%20making%20bait%20for%20potential%20scam%20targets%2C%20helping%20scammers%20identify%20gullible%20people%20in%20the%20comments%20who%20they%20can%20potentially%20extract%20money%20from.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20possibility%20is%20that%20posting%20these%20images%20is%20a%20good%20tactic%20to%20build%20up%20a%20large%20page%20audience%2C%20which%20can%20be%20lucrative.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20vague%20similarities%20among%20the%20pages%20suggest%20that%20the%20AI%20slop%20is%20being%20posted%20by%20a%20network%20of%20shady%20actors%20based%20in%20countries%20outside%20the%20US.%20It's%20spam-adjacent%20stuff%20%E2%80%94%20if%20not%20outright%20spam.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20slop%20is%20sloppy%20enough%20that%20it%20can%20sometimes%20be%20very%20funny%20%E2%80%94%20and%20there's%20even%20an%20X%20account%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FFacebookAIslop%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInsane%20Facebook%20AI%20Slop%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20dedicated%20to%20cataloging%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplatform.twitter.com%2Fwidgets.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22zxx%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FTyrMXSadDt%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FTyrMXSadDt%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Insane%20Facebook%20AI%20slop%20(%40FacebookAIslop)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FFacebookAIslop%2Fstatus%2F1806614713171656856%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJune%2028%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20embarrassing%20to%20Facebook%20that%20people%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-twitter%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETwitter%2FX%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20X!!!%20a%20place%20full%20of%20bad%20things!!!%20%E2%80%94%20are%20laughing%20at%20Meta's%20poor%20content%20moderation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20has%20been%20going%20on%20for%20quite%20a%20few%20months%20now.%20404%20Media%2C%20which%20has%20been%20diligently%20covering%20this%2C%20described%20how%20these%20images%20are%20part%20of%20a%20larger%20AI-fuelled%20%26quot%3Bzombie%20internet%26quot%3B%20full%20of%20bots%20talking%20to%20bots.%20Not%20too%20long%20ago%2C%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffacebook-ai-shrimp-jesus-zombie-internet-spam-content-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Especulated%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20why%20Meta%20hasn't%20cracked%20down%2C%20but%20considering%20nothing%20has%20seemed%20to%20change%2C%20I%20find%20myself%20wondering%20yet%20again%20%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22501fb8d8-1e46-4a8f-8576-8fae7a849914%5C%22%3EWhy%20doesn't%20Facebook%20just%20ban%20this%20slop%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20a%20few%20of%20my%20theories%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThese%20images%20don't%20technically%20violate%20any%20rules%20%E2%80%94%20no%20nudity%20or%20other%20forbidden%20imagery.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFacebook%20did%20make%20a%20warning%20label%20to%20note%20an%20image%20might%20be%20made%20with%20AI%20when%20its%20systems%20detect%20it.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EUsers%20actually%20enjoy%20this%20content%20%E2%80%94%20you%20see%20plenty%20of%20people%20in%20the%20comments%20who%20are%20probably%20duped%20and%20think%20it's%20a%20real%20image%2C%20or%20maybe%20just%20an%20interesting%20artistic%20rendition.%20Why%20mess%20with%20content%20people%20like%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFacebook%20does%20ban%20this%20stuff%2C%20but%20only%20at%20an%20account%20level%20when%20the%20account%20posting%20it%20engages%20in%20obvious%20spam%20tactics.%20But%20not%20all%20of%20the%20accounts%20are%20spamming.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESlop%20is%20often%20scam-adjacent%2C%20but%20the%20accounts%20posting%20it%20may%20not%20be%20directly%20always%20the%20ones%20doing%20the%20scams%2C%20so%20they%20don't%20get%20banned.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFacebook%20worries%20that%20banning%20this%20kind%20of%20AI%20content%20will%20set%20a%20bad%20precedent%20because%20it%20wants%20to%20encourage%20people%20to%20make%20stuff%20with%20its%20own%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-ai-llama-3-chatbot-mark-zuckerberg-existential-risks-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELlama%203%3C%2Fa%3E%20tools.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFacebook%20doesn't%20like%20the%20AI%20slop%20but%20has%20bigger%20things%20to%20worry%20about.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.404media.co%2Fhas-facebook-stopped-trying%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFacebook%20has%20stopped%20trying%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20is%20what%20Jason%20Koebler%20from%20404%20Media%20speculates.%20Meta's%20previous%20commitments%20to%20working%20with%20researchers%20and%20academics%20have%20fizzled%20away%2C%20and%20the%20scrutiny%20over%20content%20moderation%20(helped%20by%20Elon%20Musk%20lowering%20the%20bar%20to%20the%20basement)%20has%20shifted.%20Meta%20is%20penny-pinching%20and%20focusing%20on%20the%20newest%20shiny%20thing%20(AI%20tools%2C%20Instagram%2C%20the%20Metaverse)%20and%20cares%20less%20and%20less%20about%20Facebook%2C%20this%20theory%20goes.%20Basically%2C%20they%20don't%20give%20a%20shit%20anymore.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EI%20imagine%20that%20some%20combination%20of%20all%20of%20these%20might%20be%20true%20to%20some%20degree.%20A%20representative%20for%20Meta%20didn't%20reply%20to%20questions%20about%20why%20they%20don't%20simply%20ban%20AI%20slop.%20(I%20had%20recently%20also%20asked%20a%20VP%20of%20product%20at%20Meta%20about%20why%20they%20don't%20just%20ban%20this%20slop%20and%20he%20sort%20of%20changed%20the%20subject%3B%20it%20seemed%20like%20maybe%20he%20wasn't%20sure%20what%20I%20was%20talking%20about.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg-scandals-last-decade-while-running-facebook-2019-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFacebook%20has%20gone%20through%20so%20many%20different%20flavors%20of%20spammy%2Fscammy%20engagementbait%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20from%20Minions%20memes%20to%20videos%20from%20magicians%2C%20to%20actually%20dangerous%20fake%20news%20and%20extremist%20groups.%20If%20the%20AI%20slop%20isn't%20suggesting%20you%20get%20together%20in%20real%20life%20and%20overthrow%20the%20government%2C%20hey%2C%20Facebook%20has%20seen%20way%20worse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-facebook-ban-ai-slop-images-shrimp-jesus-why-2024-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719738422000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F667f34b050b021b5caeaae36%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-facebook-ban-ai-slop-images-shrimp-jesus-why-2024-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Engagement%20bait%20AI%20images%20like%20Shrimp%20Jesus%20are%20all%20over%20Facebook.%20Why%20won't%20Mark%20Zuckerberg's%20team%20just%20ban%20them%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22knotopoulos%40businessinsider.com%20(Katie%20Notopoulos)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A24%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-facebook-ban-ai-slop-images-shrimp-jesus-why-2024-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%227%20killed%20and%20dozens%20wounded%20after%20missiles%20slammed%20into%20a%20town%20in%20southern%20Ukraine%2C%20officials%20say%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719738412000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-111379255%2Cimgsize-364652.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2F7-killed-and-dozens-wounded-after-missiles-slammed-into-a-town-in-southern-ukraine-officials-say%2Farticleshow%2F111379272.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia