competition%20for%20Europe's%20next-generation%20tanks%20shapes%20up%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Multiple%20European%20arms%20makers%20are%20designing%20next-generation%20tanks%20like%20KNDS'%20Leclerc%20Evolution%20seen%20at%20a%202024%20defense%20expo%20in%20Paris.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F667f02e3d1c84a0eaca8eada%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221359%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMultiple%20European%20arms%20makers%20are%20designing%20next-generation%20tanks%20like%20KNDS'%20Leclerc%20Evolution%2C%20seen%20at%20a%202024%20defense%20expo%20in%20Paris.%3Cp%3EArtur%20Widak%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20slew%20of%20new%20tank%20designs%20are%20emerging%20from%20European%20drawing%20boards.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMany%20are%20alternatives%20to%20the%20pan-European%20tank%20envisioned%20by%20France%20and%20Germany.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20faces%C2%A0domestic%20pressure%20to%20favor%20national%20projects%20that%20benefit%20a%20nation's%20workforce.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20years%2C%20the%20European%20tank%20market%20was%20fairly%20stable.%20Germany's%20Leopard%202%20was%20the%20most%20common%20model%20in%20European%20armies%2C%20with%20Britain%2C%20France%2C%20and%20Italy%20producing%20a%20small%20number%20of%20indigenous%20models%20for%20their%20own%20armies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20a%20slew%20of%20new%20tank%20designs%20are%20emerging%20from%20European%20drawing%20boards.%20This%20is%20partly%20spurred%20by%20the%20Ukraine%20war%2C%20which%20has%20seen%20the%20most%20intense%20armored%20warfare%20in%20Europe%20since%201945.%20But%20it%20may%20also%20reflect%20a%20lack%20of%20faith%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feuro-sd.com%2F2023%2F01%2Farticles%2F29122%2Fmain-ground-combat-system-mgcs-a-status-report%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMain%20Ground%20Combat%20System%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20joint%20project%20between%20France%20and%20Germany%20to%20develop%20a%20main%20battle%20tank%20by%202040.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20seems%20that%20every%20industrial%20partner%20is%20working%20on%20its%20own%20alternative%20to%20MGCS%2C%26quot%3B%20L%C3%A9o%20P%C3%A9ria-Peign%C3%A9%2C%20a%20French%20defense%20expert%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20inevitable%20that%20a%20new%20generation%20of%20tanks%20would%20emerge%20to%20replace%20the%20late%20Cold%20War%20designs%20that%20still%20dominate%20Western%20armies%2C%20such%20as%20the%20Leopard%202%2C%20M1%20Abrams%2C%20and%20Britain's%20Challenger.%20Even%20the%20US%20Army%20is%20aiming%20for%20a%20next-generation%20version%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.defensenews.com%2Fland%2F2024%2F05%2F31%2Fa-lighter-high-tech-abrams-tank-is-taking-shape%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EM1%20Abrams%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20would%20slim%20down%20the%2070-ton%20behemoth%20to%20less%20than%2060%20tons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMCGS%20is%20meant%20to%20replace%20the%20Leopard%202%20and%20France's%20Leclerc%20as%20the%20primary%20tanks%20in%20the%20German%20and%20French%20armies.%20Both%20nations%20recently%20signed%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdsm.forecastinternational.com%2F2024%2F04%2F29%2Ffrance-and-germany-formalize-agreement-to-develop-future-main-battle-tank%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eagreement%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20begin%20development%20and%20manufacturing%20of%20a%20prototype.%20But%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20MGCS%20seemed%20like%20it%20might%20also%20replace%20the%20Leopard%202%20as%20a%20sort%20of%20pan-European%20tank.%20MGCS%20is%20supposed%20to%20be%20a%20modular%20design%20with%20advanced%20features%20such%20as%20a%20140-mm%20gun%2C%20hybrid%20propulsion%2C%20advanced%20sensors%2C%20and%20the%20ability%20to%20team%20up%20unmanned%20ground%20vehicles.%20A%20conceptual%20model%20displayed%20in%202018%20used%20a%20Leopard%202%20hull%20and%20a%20Leclerc%20turret.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20there%20are%20indications%20that%20Germany%20wants%20a%20fallback%20design%2C%20based%20on%20the%20latest%20Leopard%202A8%20model%2C%20in%20case%20MCGS%20fizzles%20out.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Leopard%202AX%2C%20an%20improved%20version%20of%20the%20Leopard%202A8%20battle%20tank%2C%20is%20being%20developed%20by%20the%20German%20defense%20industry%20at%20the%20express%20request%20of%20the%20Bundeswehr%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farmyrecognition.com%2Fnews%2Farmy-news%2Farmy-news-2024%2Fgermany-develops-next-gen-leopard-2ax-as-alternative-to-joint-mgcs-project-and-existing-leopard-2a8-tank%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EArmy%20Recognition%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20defense%20news%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20development%20also%20serves%20as%20a%20Plan%20B%20for%20Germany%20in%20case%20of%20failure%20of%20the%20Franco-German%20program%2C%20or%20even%20as%20a%20lever%20in%20future%20negotiations%2C%20thus%20confronting%20France%20with%20a%20fait%20accompli%20regarding%20the%20crucial%20decisions%20that%20remain%20to%20be%20made%2C%26quot%3B%20Army%20Recognition%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20two%20new%20designs%20are%20being%20offered%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbreakingdefense.com%2F2024%2F06%2Fknds-unveils-new-leopard-and-leclerc-main-battle-tank-concepts%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKNDS%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20joint%20venture%20between%20German%20defense%20firm%20Krauss-Maffei%20Wegmann%20%E2%80%94%20manufacturer%20of%20the%20Leopard%202%20%E2%80%94%20and%20France's%20Nexter%2C%20which%20produces%20the%20Leclerc.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Leopard%202%20A-RC%203.0%20is%20a%20modular%20design%20with%20an%20unmanned%20turret%20with%20the%20crew%20nestled%20in%20the%20hull%2C%20similar%20to%20Russia's%20T-14%20Armata.%20It%20can%20fire%20guided%20missiles%20and%20heavy%20cannon%20rounds%2C%20plus%20it%20has%20a%2030-mm%20cannon%20and%20improved%20armor%20buttressed%20by%20an%20active%20protection%20system%20to%20stop%20anti-tank%20rockets.%20Existing%20Leopard%202%20models%20can%20also%20be%20fitted%20with%20these%20features.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESignificantly%2C%20KNDS%20%26quot%3Bassesses%20the%20Leopard%202%20A-RC%203.0%20not%20only%20as%20a%20bridge%20solution%20until%20introduction%20of%20the%20next-generation%20land%20combat%20system%20MGCS%2C%20but%20also%20as%20a%20decisive%20technological%20precursor%20to%20MGCS%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.knds.com%2Fnewsroom%2Fpress-releases%2Fdetail%2Fdefining-battlefield-superiority-knds-presents-groundbreaking-technologies-in-future-land-warfare%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecompany%20press%20release%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKNDS%20is%20also%20touting%20the%20Leclerc%20Evolution%2C%20which%20is%20fitted%20with%20the%20company's%20Ascalon%20turret%20and%20gun.%20The%20company%20describes%20Ascalon%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20main%20gun%20for%20battle%20tanks%20that%20is%20more%20powerful%20than%20all%20comparable%20barrel%20weapons.%20It%20can%20fire%20compact%20and%20programmable%20ammunition%20beyond%20the%20line%20of%20sight%20with%20minimal%20wear.%20Due%20to%20its%20scalability%2C%20Ascalon%20can%20be%20fitted%20with%20any%20barrel%20from%20120%20to%20140%20mm.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20if%20the%20procurement%20picture%20wasn't%20complicated%20enough%2C%20four%20companies%20%E2%80%94%20KNDS%20Germany%2C%20KNDS%20France%2C%20Germany's%20Rheinmetall%20and%20France's%20Thales%20%E2%80%94%20have%20also%20just%20announced%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thalesgroup.com%2Fen%2Fworldwide%2Fdefence-and-security%2Fpress_release%2Findustry-signs-letter-intent-mgcs%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejoint%20venture%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20develop%20the%20MGCS.%20Yet%20Rheinmetall%20is%20also%20marketing%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgerman-arms-maker-rheinmetall-offers-ukraine-new-panther-kf51-tank-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKF51%20Panther%3C%2Fa%3E%20tank%2C%20armed%20with%20a%20new%20130-mm%20cannon.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rheinmetall.com%2Fen%2Fmedia%2Fnews-watch%2Fnews%2F2023%2F12%2F2023-12-15-panther-developement-contract-hungary%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHungary%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20signed%20a%20development%20contract%20for%20the%20Panther%2C%20which%20Rheinmetall%20has%20also%20offered%20to%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPolitical%20turmoil%20in%20France%20has%20also%20cast%20a%20shadow%20over%20MGCS%2C%20with%20far-right%20parties%20favored%20to%20win%20the%20upcoming%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.france24.com%2Fen%2Feurope%2F20240627-french-far-right-dominates-polls-three-days-ahead-of-snap-elections%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eparliamentary%20election%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BIt%20seems%20that%20even%20the%20German%20government%20believes%20the%20MGCS%20project%20could%20be%20abandoned%20if%20the%20right%20takes%20power%2C%26quot%3B%20P%C3%A9ria-Peign%C3%A9%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThings%20will%20get%20clearer%20over%20time%2C%20but%20it%20is%20obvious%20that%20both%20partners%20are%20keeping%20alternative%20solutions%20up%20their%20sleeves.%20Germany%20did%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20The%20new%20surprise%20is%20that%20even%20KNDS%20France%20seems%20to%20have%20done%20the%20same.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEuropean%20defense%20budgets%20are%20already%20being%20strained%20by%20the%20need%20to%20replenish%20depleted%20stockpiles%2C%20sending%20a%20constant%20flow%20of%20weapons%20and%20ammunition%20to%20Ukraine%2C%20and%20building%20up%20the%20manufacturing%20capacity%20to%20produce%20all%20these%20arms.%20This%20raises%20the%20question%20of%20whether%20there%20is%20enough%20money%20for%20all%20these%20various%20tank%20designs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20woes%20of%20MGCS%20also%20illustrate%20the%20problem%20that%20has%20always%20bedeviled%20joint%20European%20defense%20projects%3A%20the%20tension%20between%20saving%20money%20through%20joint%20development%2C%20versus%20domestic%20pressure%20to%20favor%20national%20projects%20that%20benefit%20a%20nation's%20manufacturers%20and%20workforce.%20If%20MGCS%20were%20to%20be%20abandoned%2C%20it%20would%20be%20a%20bad%20omen%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.airbus.com%2Fen%2Fproducts-services%2Fdefence%2Fmulti-domain-superiority%2Ffuture-combat-air-system-fcas%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFuture%20Combat%20Air%20System%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20Franco-German-Spanish%20project%20to%20develop%20a%20sixth-generation%20fighter%20as%20well%20as%20air%20combat%20drones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAbandoning%20MGCS%20would%20be%20more%20of%20a%20burden%20for%20France%20than%20for%20Germany%2C%20as%20Germany%20does%20not%20need%20France%20to%20build%20a%20new%20tank%2C%26quot%3B%20P%C3%A9ria-Peign%C3%A9%20said.%20%26quot%3BUnlike%20in%20the%20FCAS%2C%20where%20France%20can%20do%20it%20alone%20technically%20but%20lacks%20the%20money%20to%20develop%20it%20alone.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMichael%20Peck%20is%20a%20defense%20writer%20whose%20work%20has%20appeared%20in%20Forbes%2C%20Defense%20News%2C%20Foreign%20Policy%20magazine%2C%20and%20other%20publications.%20He%20holds%20an%20MA%20in%20political%20science%20from%20Rutgers%20Univ.%20Follow%20him%20on%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitter.com%2F%40mipeck1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ETwitter%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20and%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fin%2Fmipeck%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ELinkedIn%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffierce-competition-for-europes-next-generation-tanks-shapes-up-2024-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719738002000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F667f0390d1c84a0eaca8ebdc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffierce-competition-for-europes-next-generation-tanks-shapes-up-2024-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20host%20of%20defense%20contractors%20are%20offering%20alternatives%20to%20the%20pan-European%20tank%20envisioned%20by%20France%20and%20Germany.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Michael%20Peck)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffierce-competition-for-europes-next-generation-tanks-shapes-up-2024-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Military%20Cantonments%20To%20Lose%20Control%20On%20Civil%20Areas.%20What%20This%20Means%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20central%20government%20has%20stepped%20up%20the%20process%20of%20separating%20civilian%20areas%20from%20defence%20areas%2C%20and%20property%20rights%20over%20assets%20in%2013%20military%20cantonments%20will%20be%20shifted%20to%20local%20municipalities.%20This%20means%20that%20while%20military%20stations%20will%20remain%20with%20the%20forces%2C%20areas%20outside%20it%20will%20be%20transferred%20to%20the%20state%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20cantonments%2C%20the%20government%20has%20laid%20out%20broad%20guidelines%20for%20excision%20of%20civil%20areas%20and%20their%20merger%20with%20state%20municipalities.%20These%20guidelines%2C%20the%20letter%20state%2C%20were%20chalked%20in%20a%20meeting%20chaired%20by%20Defence%20Secretary%20Giridhar%20Aramane%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20propriety%20rights%20over%20all%20assets%20meant%20for%20providing%20civic%20amenities%20and%20municipal%20services%20in%20the%20excised%20area%20shall%20be%20transferred%20to%20State%20Government%2FState%20Municipalities%20free%20of%20Cost%20Assets%20%26amp%3B%20Liabilities%20of%20the%20Cantonment%20Boards%20shall%20be%20transferred%20to%20State%20Municipality%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20letter%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20clarified%20that%20the%20government%20will%20retain%20title%20rights%20where%20applicable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMunicipality%20shall%20be%20able%20to%20impose%20local%20taxes%2Ffees%20over%20such%20areas%20under%20its%20jurisdiction.%20However%2C%20while%20segregating%20the%20areas%2C%20the%20security%20concerns%20of%20Armed%20Forces%20would%20be%20given%20due%20priority%20in%20case%20there%20are%20some%20such%20privately%20held%20lands%20where%20the%20segregation%20is%20impinging%20on%20security%20of%20Military%20Station%2C%20same%20shall%20be%20considered%20in%20case%20to%20case%20basis%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20order%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Is%20This%20Being%20Done%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20sense%20in%20the%20government%20that%20cantonments%20are%20a%20part%20of%20an%20archaic%20colonial%20legacy%20and%20the%20current%20system%20deprives%20residents%20of%20these%20areas%20from%20the%20access%20to%20some%20welfare%20schemes%20of%20the%20state%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20issue%20of%20separation%20of%20civil%20and%20military%20areas%20goes%20back%20to%20the%20post-Independence%20period.%20In%201948%2C%20a%20committee%20headed%20by%20Congress%20veteran%20SK%20Patil%20had%20recommended%20the%20excision%20of%20civil%20areas%20in%20six%20Cantonments.%20But%20this%20plan%20was%20scrapped%2C%20citing%20public%20opposition%20to%20such%20a%20move.%20This%20issue%20has%20come%20up%20on%20multiple%20occasions%20since%20then%2C%20and%20the%20government's%20latest%20move%20plays%20out%20against%20that%20backdrop.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Defence%20Ministry%20owns%20nearly%2018%20lakh%20acres%20and%20is%20the%20largest%20landowner%20in%20the%20country.%20In%20the%20past%2C%20parliamentary%20panels%20have%20flagged%20the%20use%20of%20defence%20funds%20for%20non-military%20purposes%2C%20such%20as%20civic%20expenditures%20in%20civilian%20areas%20part%2