0if%20he%20coined%20the%20phrase%2C%20but%20the%20message%20is%20that%20AI%20won't%20replace%20humans%2C%20but%20it%20will%20give%20those%20who%20embrace%20it%20an%20advantage%20in%20the%20workforce.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%2012%20months%20since%20Baldwin%20shared%20his%20perspective%2C%20interest%20in%20artificial%20intelligence%20has%20only%20increased.%20A%20recent%20survey%20by%20consulting%20firm%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcompanies-using-ai-bain-survey-roi-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBain%20%26amp%3B%20Company%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20that%2085%25%20of%20the%20companies%20surveyed%20said%20adopting%20AI%20was%20a%20top-five%20priority.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20companies%20ramp%20up%20their%20AI%20offerings%20and%20begin%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmuse.insider.com%2Fstory%2F665887aa66bb31e50750af1f%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erestructuring%20their%20workforce%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20many%20are%20revisiting%20the%20question%20of%20whether%20AI%20will%20be%20a%20job%20killer%20or%20an%20enhancer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it's%20still%20the%20early%20days%20of%20AI%2C%20we%20asked%20experts%20to%20weigh%20in.%20Should%20you%20be%20more%20worried%20about%20losing%20your%20job%20to%20a%20human%20using%20AI%20or%20to%20the%20AI%20itself%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bb01e2c1-f140-4da8-adbb-a3a6776d4659%5C%22%3EWorkers%20already%20see%20the%20benefit%20of%20AI%20at%20this%20stage%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBaldwin%20said%20that%20AI%20is%20like%20a%20lawn%20mower%20or%20a%20power%20drill%20%E2%80%94%20it%20makes%20your%20job%20easier%20but%20it%20doesn't%20replace%20the%20human%20behind%20it.%20Other%20experts%20seemed%20to%20share%20a%20similar%20mindset%20that%20it's%20not%20advanced%20enough%20to%20function%20without%20direction%2C%20and%20for%20the%20most%20part%2C%20it%20helps%20people%20do%20better%20at%20their%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJasmine%20Escalera%2C%20a%20career%20coach%20at%20LiveCareer%20said%20incorporating%20AI%20can%20help%20automate%20repetitive%20tasks%20and%20%26quot%3Bfree%20up%20time%20to%20focus%20on%20upskilling.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMatt%20Betts%2C%20a%20research%20and%20development%20lead%20at%20leadership%20consulting%20firm%20RHR%20International%2C%20says%20it%20helps%20create%20efficiency%20so%20that%20consultants%20can%20focus%20on%20more%20impactful%20work%2C%20like%20interacting%20with%20the%20client.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EData%20has%20shown%20a%20similar%20trend%20that%20AI%20has%20helped%20many%20workers%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-productivity-boost-job-performance-inequality-economics-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eproduce%20high-quality%20work%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20shorter%20amount%20of%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20study%20by%20MIT%20and%20Stanford%20from%202023%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nber.org%2Fpapers%2Fw31161%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efound%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20access%20to%20AI%20increased%20productivity%20by%2014%25%20on%20average%2C%20with%20a%2034%25%20impact%20on%20new%20or%20lower-skilled%20workers.%20A%20Morgan%20Stanley%20report%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.morganstanley.com%2Fideas%2Fgenerative-ai-future-of-work%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eindicated%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20workers%20with%20multiple%20income%20streams%20who%20used%20generative%20AI%20to%20increase%20their%20productivity%20made%2021%25%20more%20on%20average%20than%20those%20who%20didn't.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20may%20also%20be%20helping%20people%20land%20jobs.%20Career%20service%20LiveCareer%20surveyed%201%2C150%20US%20workers%20in%20March%20and%20found%20that%2085%25%20of%20job%20seekers%20save%20time%20using%20AI%20for%20writing%20applications%20and%2040%25%20think%20AI%20improves%20their%20grammar%2C%20writing%2C%20and%20vocabulary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d15b8687-376d-4280-b78b-64a1b151b7df%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20loss