g%2C%20receptionists%2C%20cashiers%2C%20and%20translators%20are%20also%20roles%20that%20are%20moving%20toward%20automation%20or%20semi-automation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f65b862b-5acc-4a7f-92ef-67e8f99959cf%5C%22%3EIt's%20a%20good%20idea%20to%20skill%20up%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20March%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gspublishing.com%2Fcontent%2Fresearch%2Fen%2Freports%2F2023%2F03%2F27%2Fd64e052b-0f6e-45d7-967b-d7be35fabd16.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EGoldman%20Sachs%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20report%20found%20over%20300%20million%20jobs%20around%20the%20world%20could%20be%20impacted%20by%20AI.%20But%20it's%20impossible%20to%20predict%20how%20exactly%20they%20will%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECareer%20coach%20Escalera%20said%20the%20best%20path%20forward%20is%20to%20lean%20into%20human%20soft%20skills%20while%20skilling%20up%20and%20%26quot%3Badopting%20a%20mindset%20of%20continuous%20learning.%26quot%3B%20For%20some%20who%20are%20hiring%2C%20AI%20is%20becoming%20a%20prerequisite.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fformer-tripadvisor-ceo-red-flag-answers-hiring-interview-questions-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETripadvisor%20cofounder%20Steve%20Kaufer%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20on%20%26quot%3BThe%20Logan%20Bartlett%20Show%26quot%3B%20that%20he%20asked%20candidates%20during%20interviews%20if%20they%20tried%20out%20new%20AI%20chatbots.%20He%20said%20software%20engineers%20who%20didn't%20experiment%20with%20AI%20tools%20usually%20didn't%20get%20the%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20just%20don't%20understand%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Kaufer%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20probably%20don't%20want%20to%20work%20with%20that%20individual.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECEO%20of%20global%20event%20company%20Empire%20Entertainment%2C%20J.B.%20Miller%2C%20said%20it's%20an%20%26quot%3Bessential%20new%20skill%20set%2C%26quot%3B%20especially%20in%20an%20industry%20that%20i