ictim%20usually%20does%20not%20suspect%20any%20foul%20play.%20Thereafter%2C%20the%20woman%20orders%20something%20that%20may%20not%20be%20on%20the%20menu.%20In%20some%20case%2C%20the%20woman%20fakes%20an%20emergency%20and%20leaves%20the%20cafe%20in%20a%20hurry.%20When%20the%20bill%20comes%2C%20the%20victim%20realises%20it%20is%20several%20times%20of%20what%20he%20had%20estimated.%20On%20protesting%2C%20he%20is%20threatened%20by%20the%20cafe%20staff%20or%20bouncers.%20Left%20with%20little%20choice%2C%20he%20pays.%20Most%20people%20do%20not%20approach%20the%20police%20because%20a%20probe%20may%20reveal%20to%20his%20family%20that%20he%20is%20meeting%20people%20via%20a%20dating%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMany%20Players%20Involved%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20latest%20Delhi%20incident%20that%20targeted%20an%20IAS%20aspirant%2C%20police%20have%20arrested%20the%20cafe's%20owner%20Akshay%20Pahwa%20and%20the%20victim's%20'date'%20Afsan%20Parveen.%20Police%20said%20this%20scam%20thrives%20on%20an%20elaborate%20mechanism%20involving%20several%20players%20--%20cafe%20owners%2C%20managers%20and%20women%20who%20lure%20the%20target.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20player%20has%20a%20cut%3A%20Akshay%20Pahwa%20told%20police%20that%2015%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20bill%20goes%20to%20the%20woman%2C%2045%20per%20cent%20is%20divided%20between%20the%20managers%20and%20the%20remaining%2040%20per%20cent%20to%20the%20owners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20account%2C%20a%20Reddit%20user%20has%20said%20his%20'date'%20randomly%20ordered%20some%20firecrackers%20that%20jacked%20up%20the%20bill%20to%20over%20Rs%2040%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-embed-height%3D%5C%22316%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2Fdelhi%2Fcomments%2F15i2gk9%2Fgot_scammed_for_45k_on_tinder%2F%5C%22%3EGot%20Scammed%20for%2045k%20on%20Tinder%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cnby%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fuser%2FFinestGold%2F%5C%22%3Eu%2FFinestGold%3C%2Fa%3E