%2C%20a%20portion%20of%20the%20canopy%20collapsed%20amid%20the%20heavy%20rain%2C%20crushing%20several%20cars.%20A%20cab%20driver%2C%20who%20was%20waiting%20for%20passengers%2C%20died%20in%20the%20incident.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWaterlogging%20disrupted%20traffic%20movement%20in%20several%20areas%2C%20including%20the%20Pragati%20Maidan%20tunnel%2C%20which%20remained%20closed%20yesterday%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECivic%20officials%20have%20said%20manpower%20has%20been%20ramped%20up%20to%20handle%20waterlogging%20complaints.%20New%20Delhi%20Municipal%20Council%20(NDMC)%20vice-chairman%20Satish%20Upadhyay%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI%20that%20four%20additional%20pumps%20are%20on%20standby%20basis%20at%20Golf%20Links%20and%20Bharti%20Nagar%20areas%20that%20reeled%20due%20to%20waterlogging%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThree%20super%20suction%20machines%20mounted%20on%20vehicles%20will%20keep%20patrolling%20the%20vulnerable%20areas.%20We%20have%20also%20deployed%20additional%20staff%20and%20cancelled%20off-days%20of%20all%20staff%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BCCTV%20cameras%20are%20being%20used%20to%20monitor%20vulnerable%20areas%2C%26quot%3B%20another%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20in%20Municipal%20Corporation%20of%20Delhi%20said%20their%20central%20control%20room%20is%20working%20round%20the%20clock.%20%26quot%3BIn%20total%2C%2072%20permanent%20pumping%20stations%20were%20functional%20and%20working%20as%20per%20requirement%2C%20in%20addition%20465%20mobile%2Fsubmersible%20pumps%20of%20different%20capacities%20were%20arranged%20to%20clear%20waterlogging.%20Manpower%20was%20adequately%20deployed%20in%20tandem%20with%20machines%20for%20quick%20release%20of%20water%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20official%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELieutenant%20Governor%20VK%20Saxena%20has%20inspected%20the%20most-affected%20areas%20and%20drainage%20systems%2C%20a%20statement%20said.%20Mr%20Saxena%20found%20drains%20choked%20with%20garbage%2C%20debris%20and%20sludge%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWeather%20experts%20have%20flagged%20extreme%20weather%20events%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20over%20the%20past%20few%20years.%20They%20have%20noted%20that%20Delhi%20receives%20around%20650%20mm%20of%20rainfall%20during%20Monsoon.%20And%20weather%20data%20shows%20the%20city%20received%20one-third%20of%20this%20on%20the%20first%20day%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719720060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fhkokmo4o_delhi-rain_625x300_30_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fdelhi-rain-delhi-waterlogging-delhi-braces-for-more-rain-after-11-dead-records-broken-by-monsoon-entry-6000954%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Delhi%20residents%2C%20still%20recovering%20from%20the%20after-effects%20of%20the%20record-breaking%20downpour%20on%20Friday%2C%20must%20brace%20for%20more%20rain.%20The%20weather%20office%20has%20issued%20an%20orange%20alert%20for%20the%20national%20capital%2C%20predicting%20heavy%20rainfall%20today%20and%20tomorrow.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fdelhi-rain-delhi-waterlogging-delhi-braces-for-more-rain-after-11-dead-records-broken-by-monsoon-entry-6000954%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fdelhi-rain-delhi-waterlogging-delhi-braces-for-more-rain-after-11-dead-records-broken-by-monsoon-entry-6000954%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fdelhi-rain-delhi-waterlogging-delhi-braces-for-more-rain-after-11-dead-records-broken-by-monsoon-entry-6000954%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22T20%20World%20Cup%202024%20final%3A%2013-yr%20drought%20ended%2C%20India%20lifts%20cup%20in%20Barbados%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719719854000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fb