_articleshow%2F111374670.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UK%20Elections%202024%3A%20Rishi%20Sunak's%20India%20Connection%20In%2010%20Points%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERishi%20Sunak%20scripted%20history%20on%20October%2025%2C%202022%2C%20when%20he%20became%20the%20first%20Indian-origin%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20the%20United%20Kingdom.%20In%20the%20upcoming%20July%204%20elections%2C%20Mr%20Sunak's%20Conservative%20Party%20is%20facing%20a%20major%20challenge%20from%20the%20Opposition%20Labour%20Party%2C%20led%20by%20Keir%20Starmer.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EAhead%20of%20the%20crucial%20polls%2C%20here's%20a%20look%20at%20the%2010%20points%20about%20Rishi%20Sunak's%20connection%20with%20India%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn1.%20Rishi%20Sunak%20was%20born%20on%20May%2012%2C%201980%2C%20in%20Southampton%2C%20Hampshire.%20His%20parents%20--%20Yashvir%20Sunak%20and%20Usha%20Sunak%20--%20are%20of%20Indian%20descent.%20While%20his%20father%20was%20a%20National%20Health%20Service%20general%20practitioner%2C%20his%20mother%2C%20Usha%2C%20ran%20a%20chemist%20shop.%20Both%20of%20them%20migrated%20from%20East%20Africa%20to%20the%20UK%20during%20the%201960s.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn2.%20For%20his%20studies%2C%20Mr%20Sunak%20went%20to%20Winchester%20College%20and%20studied%20Politics%2C%20Philosophy%20and%20Economics%20at%20Oxford%20University.%20Further%2C%20he%20was%20also%20a%20Fulbright%20Scholar%20at%20Stanford%20University%20in%20the%20US%2C%20where%20he%20studied%20for%20his%20MBA.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn3.%20Rishi%20Sunak%20is%20married%20to%20Akshata%20Murty%2C%20the%20daughter%20of%20Infosys%20chief%20Narayana%20Murthy%20and%20Sudha%20Murty%2C%20who%20is%20a%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP.%20Together%2C%20Rishi%20and%20Akshata%20have%20two%20daughters%20-%20Krishna%20and%20Anoushka.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn4.%C2%A0%20He%20has%20served%20as%20a%20Member%20of%20Parliament%20from%20Richmond%20(Yorks)%20since%202015.%20He%20earlier%20became%20the%20first%20UK%20parliamentarian%20to%20take%20oath%20as%20an%20MP%20on%20the%20Bhagavad%20Gita%20in%20the%20Parliament.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn5.%20Being%20a%20Hindu%2C%20he%20has%20often%20been%20vocal%20about%20his%20heritage%20and%20how%20his%20family%20reminded%20him%20about%20their%20values%20and%20culture.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn6.%20He%20celebrated%20Diwali%20with%20his%20wife%20and%20family%20at%2010%20Downing%20Street%20and%20even%20hosted%20a%20reception%20last%20year%20for%20the%20Indian%20diaspora%2C%20parliamentarians%2C%20entrepreneurs%20and%20Bollywood%20celebrities.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn7.%20Before%20becoming%20the%20UK%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20Rishi%20Sunak%20would%20often%20visit%20Bengaluru%20with%20his%20wife%20and%20two%20children%20to%20meet%20his%20in-laws.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn8.%20While%20he%20was%20campaigning%20for%20the%20PM's%20post%20in%202022%2C%20Mr%20Sunak%20was%20criticised%20for%20his%20lavish%20house%2C%20expensive%20suits%2C%20and%20shoes.%20However%2C%20he%20later%20said%20that%20the%20Bhagavad%20Gita%20often%20rescues%20him%20during%20stressful%20situations%2C%20besides%20reminding%20him%20to%20be%20dutiful.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn9.%20Like%20most%20Indians%2C%20Sunak%2C%20too%2C%20likes%20to%20play%20cricket%20to%20stay%20fit.%20In%20April%20this%20year%2C%20he%20surprised%20netizens%20by%20joining%20the%20country's%20cricket%20team%20for%20a%20net%20session.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn10.%20Besides%20being%20a%20part%20of%20politics%2C%20Mr%20Sunak%20has%20had%20a%20successful%20business%20career%20as%20well.%20He%20co-founded%20a%20firm%2C%20while%20working%20with%20companies%20from%20Silicon%20Valley%20to%20Bengaluru%2C%20according%20to%20reports.%20In%20May%2C%20it%20was%20reported%20that%20the%20personal%20wealth%20of%20Rishi%20Sunak%20and%20his%20wife%20rose%20by%20122%20million%20pounds%20last%20year%20and%20reached%20651%20million%20pounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719717780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvi