eatening%20accident.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20she%20sits%20down%20with%3Cstrong%3E%20The%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20to%20recall%20%E2%80%9Cone%20of%20the%20toughest%20phases%20of%20her%20life%E2%80%9D%2C%20she%20finds%20it%20almost%20impossible%20to%20relive%20the%20details.%20This%20is%20due%20to%20two%20reasons%20%E2%80%94%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20accident%2C%20Sakshi%20was%20unconscious%20for%2020%20days%20and%20the%20things%20she%20does%20remember%20are%20almost%20too%20painful%20to%20reminisce%20about.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20time%20Sakshi%20revisits%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F249129%2Fsanjay-dubey-pizza-pasta-accident-up-delhi-food-stall-entrepreneur-artificial-limb-inspirational-vid01%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20incident%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20her%20carefree%20life%20before%20it%2C%20it%20is%20almost%20like%20knocking%20on%20an%20old%20friend%E2%80%99s%20door%2C%20but%20one%20who%20isn%E2%80%99t%20home%20anymore.%20You%20see%2C%20a%20new%20Sakshi%20was%20reborn%20following%20the%20accident%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%98Sakshi%202.0%E2%80%99%2C%20as%20her%20mother%20calls%20it%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0%20and%20this%20version%20is%20here%20to%20stay.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20journey%20from%20being%20a%20second-year%20MBBS%20student%20who%20met%20with%20a%20horrifying%20accident%20leaving%20her%20with%20multiple%20broken%20bones%20to%20now%20being%20a%20practising%20orthopaedic%20surgeon%20has%20been%20a%20telling%20one.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%2010%25%20chance%20of%20survival%2C%E2%80%9D%20her%20doctors%20had%20declared.%20But%20it%20was%20Sakshi%E2%80%99s%20willpower%20that%20contested%20this%20statistic.%20And%20this%20is%20her%20story.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20call%20that%20changed%20many%20lives%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20their%20Ahmedabad%20home%2C%20Sakshi%E2%80%99s%20parents%2C%20Sne