inted%2Fsad%20you%20are.%E2%80%9D%20This%20instantly%20makes%20the%20child%20feel%20understood%20and%20they%20are%20more%20open%20and%20trusting%20with%20their%20parents.%20This%20also%20builds%20their%20emotional%20intelligence%20where%20they%20learn%20how%20to%20handle%20feelings%20in%20a%20healthy%20way.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%225%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EMeeting%20needs%20changes%20kids%E2%80%99%20behaviour%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%E2%80%93%20What%20every%20parent%20wishes%20for%20is%20a%20magic%20wand%20to%20make%20their%20child%20%E2%80%9Cbehave%E2%80%9D.%20They%20actually%20have%20one%3A%20understanding%20the%20reason%20behind%20behaviours.%20When%20we%20meet%20our%20children%E2%80%99s%20needs%2C%20their%20behaviour%20changes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EParents%20find%20it%20valuable%20to%20make%20the%20shift%20from%2C%20%E2%80%9CDon%E2%80%99t%20behave%20like%20this%E2%80%9D%20to%20playing%C2%A0%20detective%20and%20asking%20themselves%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20is%20my%20child%20doing%20this%3F%E2%80%9D%20This%20has%20helped%20a%20great%20number%20of%20parents%20defuse%20situations%20that%20could%20have%20turned%20explosive!%20They%20say%2C%20%E2%80%9CKnowing%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F334684%2Fmumbai-ca-dad-starts-a-toy-rental-business-rents-affordable-toys-for-kids%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echild%E2%80%99s%20developmental%20needs%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20must%20for%20every%20parent.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2F1_11zon-1-1719403506.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lessons%20from%20parenting%20workshops%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2F1_11zon-1-1719403506.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2F1_11zon-1-1719403506-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2F1_11zon-1-1719403506-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2F1_11zon-1-1719403506-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2F1_11zon-1-1719403506-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-354407%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%226%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20childhood%20experiences%20impact%20my%20parenting%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%E2%80%93%20Why%20do%20I%20react%20so%20strongly%20to%20certain%20behaviours%20of%20my%20child%3F%20Sometimes%20the%20same%20behaviour%20does%20not%20bother%20my%20spouse.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDiscovering%20how%20much%20their%20own%20childhood%20experience%20affects%20the%20way%20they%20parent%20is%20an%20%E2%80%98aha%E2%80%99%20moment%20for%20most%20attendees.%C2%A0%20We%20tend%20to%20repeat%20patterns%20of%20authority%20and%20violence%2C%20because%20we%20have%20not%20thought%20about%20how%20it%20harmed%20us.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20go%20back%20to%20being%20a%20child%20and%20recall%20how%20hurt%20or%20humiliated%20I%20have%20felt%20even%20with%20just%20one%20slap%2C%20then%20that%20memory%20reminds%20me%20not%20to%20do%20the%20same%20to%20my%20child.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%227%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ERespect%20a%20child%3F%20Shouldn%E2%80%99t%20the%20child%20respect%20the%20adult%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20It%20is%20a%20huge%20mindset%20alteration%20in%20our%20adult-centric%20societies%20to%20acknowledge%20that%20respect%20is%20a%20two-way%20street.%20Parents%20observe%20that%20when%20they%20respect%20their%20children%2C%20listen%20to%20their%20opinions%20and%20w