20the%20solar-powered%20fans%20could%20only%20last%20till%209%3A30.%20We%20had%20to%20turn%20on%20the%20generator%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20night.%20If%20the%20capacity%20is%20increased%2C%20we%20will%20be%20able%20to%20retire%20to%20bed%20and%20sleep%20peacefully%20after%20a%20hectic%20day%20providing%20quality%20service%20to%20the%20people.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20healthcare%20provider%20believes%20the%20capacity%20must%20be%20increased%2C%20Riturekha%20says%20that%20with%20the%20additional%20support%20of%20solar%20energy%2C%20the%20floating%20health%20clinic%20is%20successfully%20catering%20to%20about%2010%2C000%20patients%20in%20the%20district%20every%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDue%20to%20soil%20erosion%20and%20regular%20flooding%20in%20the%20region%2C%20it%20has%20been%20a%20challenge%20to%20build%20a%20permanent%20structure%20in%20these%20places%20which%20leads%20to%20medical%20apathy%20for%20the%20residents.%20But%20with%20these%20boat%20clinics%2C%20we%20are%20able%20to%20bridge%20the%20healthcare%20divide%20in%20remote%20areas%20of%20the%20islands%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Riturekha%20Barua%20and%20Dr%20Saddam%20Hussain.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719404622000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fassam-2-1719399558.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D354362%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22When%20reporting%20from%20rural%20parts%20of%20Assam%2C%20Sanjoy%20Hazarika%20noticed%20the%20intense%20need%20for%20a%20sustained%20healthcare%20system%20in%20the%20region.%20In%20collaboration%20with%20the%20National%20Rural%20Health%20Mission%2C%20his%20non-profit%2C%20C-NES%2C%20launched%20boat%20clinics%20in%202005%20to%20bridge%20the%20healthcare%20divide.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F354362%2Fboat-health-clinics-solar-energy-on-brahmaputra-river-assam-sanjoy-hazarika%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20To%20Make%20a%20UPSC%20CSE%20Prep%20Timetable%20That%20Works%3F%20IAS%20Officer%20Shares%20Her%20Secret%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E7%3A10%20pm%3Cbr%3E10%20October%2C%202022%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20results%20of%20the%20Union%20Public%20Service%20Commission%20(UPSC)%20Civil%20Service%20Exam%20(CSE)%202021%20were%20announced%2C%20bringing%20squeals%20of%20happiness%2C%20tears%2C%20and%20bear%20hugs%20to%20the%20Pandey%20household%20in%20Jamtara%2C%20Jharkhand.%20Taruni%20had%20cleared%20the%20exam%20and%20was%20on%20her%20way%20to%20becoming%20a%20civil%20servant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20celebration%20was%20even%20more%20remarkable%20because%20this%20was%20her%20first%20and%20last%20attempt%3B%20at%2032%2C%20she%20prepared%20for%20the%20exam%20in%20just%20six%20months%20without%20any%20coaching!%20She%20accomplished%20this%20feat%20through%20a%20self-devised%20strategy%20that%20included%20meticulous%20planning%2C%20detailed%20note-taking%2C%20and%20a%20strict%20timetable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-06-20-at-11.59.14-1719322998.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Taruni's%20life%20goals%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-06-20-at-11.59.14-1719322998.jpeg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-06-20-at-11.59.14-1719322998-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-06-20-at-11.59.14-1719322998-500x375.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-06-20-at-11.59.14-1719322998-768x576.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-06-20-at-11.59.14-1719322998-150x113.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-354319%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ETaruni%E2%80%99s%20life%20goals%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20referred%20to%20YouTube%20videos%20and%20prepared%20notes%20based%20on%20them.%20With%20just%20four%20months%20of%20preparation%20for%20the%20prelims%20and%20two%20months%20for%20the%20mains%2C%20she%20cleared%20her%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F353815%2Fias-officer-ashish-kumar-singhal-jaipur-cleared-upsc-cse-after-four-failures-topper%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUPSC%20CSE%20prelims%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20secured%20rank%2014%20in%20the%20Consolidated%20Reserve%20List%20in%20the%20CSE%20mains%202021.%20She%20is%20currently%20an%20officer%20in%20training%20with%20the%20Indian%20Communications%20Finance%20Services%20(IP%26amp%3BTAFS)%20in%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Communications.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20how%20she%20planned%20her%20studies%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETips%20for%20creating%20an%20effective%20study%20plan%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaruni%20Pandey%20(34)%2C%20a%20proponent%20of%20self-study%20since%20childhood%2C%20always%20relied%20on%20putting%20things%20on%20paper.%20Her%20timetable%20was%20not%20based%20on%20strict%20timings%20but%20rather%20on%20a%20to-do%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20made%20weekly%20and%20monthly%20plans.%20The%20most%20important%20thing%20to%20remember%20is%20to%20be%20flexible%20as%20things%20change%20at%20any%20given%20point%20in%20time.%20I%20used%20to%20have%20a%20daily%20target%20of%20finishing%2C%20say%2C%20a%20chapter%20or%20a%20particular%20portion%20of%20a%20subject%2C%E2%80%9D%20Taruni%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20daily%20plan%20included%20a%20mix%20of%20subjects%20%E2%80%94%20one%20arts%20and%20one%20science%20%E2%80%94%20which%20helped%20break%20the%20monotony.%20She%20stuck%20a%20cardboard%20sheet%20with%20her%20plan%2C%20listing%20the%20subjects%20and%20organising%20them%20into%20six%20columns.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20first%20column%20was%20study%2C%20second%20notes%2C%20third%20was%20revision%20one%2C%20fourth%20was%20revision%20two%2C%20fifth%20was%20crisp%20notes%2C%20and%20sixth%20was%20final%20revision.%20For%20each%20subject%2C%20I%20would%20place%20a%20tick%20once%20I%20completed%20each%20step%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FInfographic-website-10-1719322769.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Taruni's%20time%20table%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FInfographic-website-10-1719322769.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FInfographic-website-10-1719322769-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FInfographic-website-10-1719322769-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FInfographic-website-10-1719322769-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FInfographic-website-10-1719322769-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-354316%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ETaruni%E2%80%99s%20time%20table.%20List%20down%20the%20subjects%20and%20tick%20the%20items%20after%20completion.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3